sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Owner
  participant A as App
  participant L as SwiftData
  participant Q as Pending Queue
  participant FS as Firestore
  U->>A: Share entry to selected Circle(s)
  A->>L: Set visibility=circle and sharedCircleIds
  A->>Q: Enqueue updateVisibility/updateEntry
  Q->>FS: Idempotent owner-authorized update
  FS-->>Q: Rule-validated result
